Sentencas: The effects of Al2O3 on (1 - x)[SrO-SiO2-B2O3]-xAl(2)O(3) (SASB, x=0, 0.02, 0.04, 0.06, 0.08, and 0.1) sealing glasses for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) have been investigated to determine the proper amount of Al2O3 for the application of the SASB glasses to a SOFC sealant.
Titulo: Effects of Al2O3 on (1-x)[SrO-SiO2-B2O3]-xAl2O3 glass sealant for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The structural, thermal, mechanical and adhesion properties were determined by using DTA, TMA, XRD, SEM, and Raman spectroscopy.
Titulo: Effects of Al2O3 on (1-x)[SrO-SiO2-B2O3]-xAl2O3 glass sealant for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: It is found that the thermal expansion coefficients of the glasses and crystallized samples are 8.0-11.0 x 10(-6) degrees C-1 and similar to 10.0 x 10(-6) degrees C-1, respectively, which are within the required values for the SOFC sealant.
Titulo: Effects of Al2O3 on (1-x)[SrO-SiO2-B2O3]-xAl2O3 glass sealant for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The change of mode population in Raman scattering analysis shows that Al(2)o(3) acts as a network modifier.
Titulo: Effects of Al2O3 on (1-x)[SrO-SiO2-B2O3]-xAl2O3 glass sealant for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: When annealed at 800 degrees C, the glasses with x=0 and 0.1 start to crystallize in 5 h, but the sample with x=0.6 mostly remains as a glass phase even after 50 h, and this crystallization behavior has a close relationship with adhesion properties.
Titulo: Effects of Al2O3 on (1-x)[SrO-SiO2-B2O3]-xAl2O3 glass sealant for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: Comparing the cross-sectional views of SEM images between x=0 and x=0.06, the sample with x=0.06 shows homogeneous morphologies with good adhesion and clean surface boundaries between the sample and substrate.
Titulo: Effects of Al2O3 on (1-x)[SrO-SiO2-B2O3]-xAl2O3 glass sealant for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: But for the x=0 case, the boundaries are not clearly defined and devitrifications with heterogeneous morphologies exist.
Titulo: Effects of Al2O3 on (1-x)[SrO-SiO2-B2O3]-xAl2O3 glass sealant for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell
